title: chapter2_SSSpam_CaptainsTable_George1
tags:
---
George: I bet you've never been on a ship as fine as this before, little mouse. 
George: Your mind is probably blown by all this luxury.
Captain Drake: Oh, we have plenty of time. 
Captain Drake: If that's the case, then why don't you give your friend a tour, Lord Sullivan?
