Gigi: Unfortunately, they did manage to take some of the ship's Familiar crew with them but it seems like our public defeat of their leader made them abandon the rest of their scheme. 
    -> Player: I'm glad we managed to protect all these Familiars.
        Gigi: That will teach them to underestimate Adventurers like us... 
        Gigi: I mean, like me!
    -> Player: I wish we could have stopped them escaping.
        Gigi:  It's not your fault. You did what you could. 
Gigi: We should be almost at Omen City Port. 
Gigi: Let's rejoin the others upstairs.
===

